    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――八月二十八日　夜",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あわわわわっ、悩んでる間に時間が……！\nあと三時間しかない……今からどうすればいいの！？",
      "startTime": 7.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4676.750032099999,
          "startTime": 12.0767500321
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "愛。そんなに慌てなくても大丈夫よ。気持ちのこもった\nものなら、なんでも嬉しいわ。お祝いの言葉とかね",
      "startTime": 16.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "り、り、莉央さん！？　な、な、なんのことですか？\n別に、そんなっ、プレゼントで悩んでたりなんてっ",
      "startTime": 24.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん。じゃあ、愛は私にプレゼントをあげる気は\nないって言うこと？　ふぅん、なるほどね～",
      "startTime": 33.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "ち、ちち違いますあげる気でした！　葵さんと怜さん\nみたいに素敵なものを用意出来れば良かったんですが",
      "startTime": 42.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "冗談よ。もう、汗かき過ぎ。愛も悩んでくれたんでしょ\nそうね、ちょうど私、小腹が空いてきちゃったんだけど",
      "startTime": 54.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6500.000001700002,
          "startTime": 60.9666666684
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん……！　では、この小美山愛、真心を込めて\nラーメンを作ります！　数時間待っていただけますと！",
      "startTime": 64.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、おねが……って長いわよ！　夜が明けるじゃない\nじゃあラーメン以外……いえ、一緒に作りましょうか",
      "startTime": 74.6000040691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "オムライスですか～！　絶対、美味しくなりますね！\nでも、いいんですか？　別に、私一人で作っても……",
      "startTime": 86.7000040691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に作った方が楽しいでしょ\n今日の主役が言ってるんだから、いいのよ",
      "startTime": 93.9333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、有り物で作るから、あまり味の保証は出来ないわ\nとりあえずソースを作ったけど……やっぱり微妙ね",
      "startTime": 102.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "普通に美味しいと思いますけど……\nえ、ちょっと、莉央さん！？　作り直すんですか！？",
      "startTime": 109.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "違う！　一つ大人になった私はこんなものじゃないのよ\n岡山の喫茶店の娘としてのプライドが許さないわ！",
      "startTime": 121.1333221436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "あの、もう誕生日終わっちゃいましたけど……\nいいのかな……最後まで手伝うけど……",
      "startTime": 130.3269199812,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bird-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5806.399110699999,
          "startTime": 136.1333190919
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "ん～、美味しい！　お父さんの味そっくりだわ！\nレシピ通りに作っても、今までなぜか似なかったのに",
      "startTime": 143.5666493734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "隠し味とかですかね？　ふふふ、こんな奇跡が起こる\nなんて。これが、莉央さんが子供の頃に食べてた味",
      "startTime": 152.899995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "っ、お父さん……。ありがとう、愛。付き合ってくれて\nなんだか、また一つ大人になれた気がするわ",
      "startTime": 166.799995931,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.342615799984,
          "startTime": 171.0333385468
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "え、二人とも何してるんですか？　今日、早朝から\nお仕事ですよね。葵さん先に行っちゃいましたよ？",
      "startTime": 175.0666788737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "startTime": 179.2000052135,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}